Description: Native Odoo dashboard, task timer and desktop notifications
 Odoo Companion connects directly to your own Odoo instance using Odoo's
 JSON-RPC external API. It provides native desktop notifications, a GTK4
 dashboard with charts, notification history, a background task timer,
 live attendance status in the system tray, and clickable, filterable
 module pages (Sales, CRM, Project, Purchase, Inventory, Accounting,
 Expenses, Recruitment, Time Off, Activities, Attendance, Timesheets).
 .
 Credentials are stored in the system keyring (libsecret); data is fetched
 directly from your own Odoo server and never sent to any third party.
